* [SecurityHonestyGovernance], [LocalIdentityConsumption] -(Gates)> [recommendation_candidate], [shared_packet], [outside]

(social_periphery_interest_fabric_realization) :local_interest_digest: /privacy_scope and explanation_gate/ |network_outside|
